                                       Q2. Write a program In C++ to accept temperature in Celsius and convert to Fahrenheit?

ANSWER :-
 
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
float cel , far;
cout<<"Enter Temperature in Celsius : ";
cin>>cel;
far=(cel * 9.0) / 5.0 + 32;
cout<<"Temperature in Fahrenheit is : " <<far<<endl;
return 0;
}

